{"product_id":"pork-baby-back-ribs","title":"Pork Baby Back Ribs","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSucculent pork baby back ribs prepared and par-cooked for fast, easy cooking. Prepared in our signature style, with our classic dry rub, and marinated in our Sweet BBQ to ensure the juiciest meat. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe ribs you never knew you needed, but glad you found. Quite frankly, the tastiest ribs you'll find the in the UK! \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eWhat You Get:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e2 x Racks of Ribs (Approx. 800g)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eHow to cook\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eGrill\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCook these ribs over a hot fire to crisp up the sauces, place meat side up to start and baste and turn regularly \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eOven \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eTotal cooking time - 20 minutes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003ePreheat oven to 200(C), place ribs in a suitable oven dish and baste with our BBQ sauce generously. After 10 minutes, remove and baste again. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"800g (Approx.)","offers":[{"title":"Signature Dry Rub","offer_id":42980051222757,"sku":"","price":12.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false},{"title":"Sticky BBQ","offer_id":42963572752613,"sku":null,"price":12.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0645\/6197\/1429\/products\/babybackribs1.jpg?v=1653677465","url":"https:\/\/meatshed.co.uk\/products\/por